    },
    "3": {
      "id": 3,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/xueliyuenzuo3.xueliyuenzuo3'",
      "text": "淡入淡出效果测试4",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 1,
      "auto_play_time": 20,
      "dialogue_sound": "dialog165000202",
      "next_picture": 4
    },
    "4": {
      "id": 4,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/xueliyuenzuo4.xueliyuenzuo4'",
      "text": "这个魔法失败过很多次，但这一次，请一定要成功啊。嘿！「魔力果超级大爆发」——",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 1,
      "auto_play_time": 20,
      "background_music": "6",
      "next_picture": 5
    },
    "5": {
      "id": 5,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/xueliyuenzuo5.xueliyuenzuo5'",
      "text": "老大！怎、怎么办……那个菜鸟研究员把噩梦龙息帕尔变没了！",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 2,
      "auto_play_time": 20,
      "next_picture": 6
    },
    "6": {
      "id": 6,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/xueliyuenzuo6.xueliyuenzuo6'",
      "text": "到手的传说精灵，没了我怎么给上面交差！",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 2,
      "auto_play_time": 20,
      "next_picture": 7
    },
    "7": {
      "id": 7,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/xueliyuenzuo7.xueliyuenzuo7'",
      "text": "好厉害的马戏表演！",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 2,
      "auto_play_time": 20,
      "next_picture": 8
    },
    "8": {
      "id": 8,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/xueliyuenzuo8.xueliyuenzuo8'",
      "text": "你好，我叫希洛。很高兴认识你！既然你的脚下的咕噜老是转个不停，我那就叫你小轱辘好了。",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 2,
      "auto_play_time": 20,
      "next_picture": 9
    },
    "9": {
      "id": 9,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/xueliyuenzuo9.xueliyuenzuo9'",
      "text": "加油，小轱辘，就快到终点了！你是最厉害的！",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 2,
      "auto_play_time": 20
    },
    "101": {
      "id": 101,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/S1_season_task_slide1.S1_season_task_slide1'",
      "text": "小轱辘，等我学会最厉害的魔法，就回来找你！",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 2,
      "auto_play_time": 10,
      "background_music": "1",
      "next_picture": 102
    },
    "102": {
      "id": 102,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/S1_season_task_slide2.S1_season_task_slide2'",
      "text": "作为辛苦的码头小子，每天下班，弗雷姆都能等到可爱的法尔，和它一起玩耍。",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 1,
      "auto_play_time": 15,
      "next_picture": 103
    },
    "103": {
      "id": 103,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/S1_season_task_slide3.S1_season_task_slide3'",
      "text": "渐渐地，法尔将弗雷姆视作了最亲密的主人；在弗雷姆眼中，法尔亦是世界上最可爱的小狗。",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 1,
      "auto_play_time": 5,
      "background_music": "5",
      "next_picture": 104
    },
    "104": {
      "id": 104,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/S1_season_task_slide4.S1_season_task_slide4'",
      "text": "往日码头逐渐废弃，水手也不再往来。只有法尔固执地守在月牙湖畔，遥遥无期地等待主人的归来。",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 1,
      "auto_play_time": 5,
      "next_picture": 105
    },
    "105": {
      "id": 105,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/S1_season_task_slide5.S1_season_task_slide5'",
      "text": "百年前，当信仰者们纷纷涌入这座台地的时刻。作为台地原住民的阿特岚，尚未做好接纳他们的准备。",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 2,
      "auto_play_time": 5,
      "next_picture": 106
    },
    "106": {
      "id": 106,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/S1_season_task_slide6.S1_season_task_slide6'",
      "text": "直到，风雪呼啸扑向村落的那天……阿特岚振翅而起，奋力将砸向人们的积雪扫入山崖之下。",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 1,
      "auto_play_time": 5,
      "next_picture": 107
    },
    "107": {
      "id": 107,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/S1_season_task_slide7.S1_season_task_slide7'",
      "text": "人们的感激与崇拜，化作了村落的「星霜花塔」。这是信仰者们，对阿特岚阁下无私守护的敬意。",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 2,
      "auto_play_time": 5,
      "next_picture": 108
    },
    "108": {
      "id": 108,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/S1_season_task_slide8.S1_season_task_slide8'",
      "text": "当误会成为传说，当事鸟阿特岚却哭笑不得——它不过做了举爪之劳而已。",
      "mask_effect_type": 1,
      "picture_switch_type": 1,
      "auto_play_time": 5,
      "background_music": "2",
      "next_picture": 109
    },
    "109": {
      "id": 109,
      "picture": "Texture2D'/Game/NewRoco/Modules/System/TeachingManual/Raw/Icon/S1_season_task_slide9.S1_season_task_slide9'",
